                        <filepath class="+ topic/ph sw-d/filepath " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/startup_dita_project.dita" xtrc="filepath:10;73:35">custom-settings/learned-words/en.tdi</filepath> file.</li>
                <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/startup_dita_project.dita" xtrc="li:11;74:21">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/startup_dita_project.dita" xtrc="uicontrol:9;74:36">Editor</uicontrol> / <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/startup_dita_project.dita" xtrc="uicontrol:10;74:68">Edit Modes</uicontrol> /
