                <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/startup_dita_project.dita" xtrc="li:13;79:21">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/startup_dita_project.dita" xtrc="uicontrol:14;79:36">Document Type Association</uicontrol> preferences page disables
