            you should download the project template (<codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/startup_dita_project.dita" xtrc="codeph:2;177:63">.zxpr</codeph> file) from the project
                <xref href="https://github.com/oxygenxml/DITA-Startup-Project/releases" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/startup_dita_project.dita" xtrc="xref:22;179:48"><?ditaot usertext?>releases page</xref> and <xref href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-editor/topics/create-your-own-templates.html#create-your-own-templates" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/startup_dita_project.dita" xtrc="xref:23;181:48"><?ditaot usertext?>set it as a new document template</xref>.</p>
